species.name: Corellian Human
species.description: Humans are the dominant species on Corellia. Though Corellians have a reputation for possessing quick wits and even quicker reflexes, there are no significant biological or physiological differences between the human natives of Corellia and humans elsewhere in the galaxy. They are genetically and anatomically as varies as most other human populations, though they tend to be slightly taller than average, and there are an unusually high number of Force sensitives among certain Corellian bloodlines.
species.startSkills: Begin with 1 rank in Piloting (Planetary) or Piloting (Space), and may train Piloting up to rank 3 during character creation.
